feedback: Interesting, well compensated study, thank you.
Everything worked well; no issues. Best of luck with your research!
No problems, the survey worked well. Thank you.
The survey was fine. It was straight forward and I understood the directions and questions

I was slightly conflicted about the Beetle's intelligence. I believe even insects have certain instincts that they follow, and to me instincts are a form of intention, and intention is a form of consciousness. Just something I was considering during the study.
While it's not impossible for a robot to have human equivalent cognition, the technology simply isn't there yet.
Quality of pay probably correlates with quality of data.  I know it does in our lab.
Thank you and no other comments.
